{"tid":1195522,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一直都想知道點解要遊「行」","createTime":"2019-06-09T15:50:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T05:45:21.000Z","uid":12633,"like":18,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"f0df331c87f80c4b905d2f622e198c5cb4507dd4","tid":1195522,"uid":12633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T15:50:06.000Z","msg":"以前遊行係為左吸引市民關注，並且表現民意；<br />\n<br />\n但而家其實有好多網絡/街站宣傳已經達到「吸引關注」既目的；而要表示民意，可唔可以唔「行」呢？<br />\n<br />\n由3點行到夜晚9點，其實個個人既體力都差唔多用盡，市民各有自己既原因要早啲返屋企；<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">民怨 與 氣勢已經俾遊行既長路、炎熱既天氣所耗盡。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">點解仲要行？</span><br />\n點解要由炮台山行去金鐘？<br />\n一黎先行既人要等龍尾，二黎龍尾又要等前面既人行左先，消耗晒我地既心力。<br />\n<br />\n最後去到夜晚9點，個個又餓又熱又攰，點衝？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">下次可唔可以一黎就立法會集合，把握體力&amp;民憤，一鼓作氣？</span>"},{"pid":"54307f207628cb9f9af8710fc46b5ab4abdf4da1","tid":1195522,"uid":12633,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T04:25:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"379c959a455a3c185ac2661616431a186b6ee4e5","tid":1195522,"uid":3177,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T04:32:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://medium.com/%E9%95%B7%E9%BE%8D%E7%94%B0139%E8%99%9F/%E9%BB%9E%E8%A7%A3%E6%B0%91%E9%99%A3%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C%E9%9B%86%E6%9C%83%E5%AE%8C%E9%83%BD%E4%B8%80%E5%AE%9A%E8%A6%81%E6%95%A3%E6%B0%B4-149e32d0f678?fbclid=IwAR0yZ4ZRBh8b1sA75x7uXFa7RIBP6MF55M0NU1kRGiXddApYHCvizdJaNGs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedium.com%2F%25E9%2595%25B7%25E9%25BE%258D%25E7%2594%25B0139%25E8%2599%259F%2F%25E9%25BB%259E%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E6%25B0%2591%25E9%2599%25A3%25E9%2581%258A%25E8%25A1%258C%25E9%259B%2586%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%25AE%258C%25E9%2583%25BD%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%25AE%259A%25E8%25A6%2581%25E6%2595%25A3%25E6%25B0%25B4-149e32d0f678%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0yZ4ZRBh8b1sA75x7uXFa7RIBP6MF55M0NU1kRGiXddApYHCvizdJaNGs&d=sUHHPMw%2FtTWAhlV0Ap%2Bq4ywbHaueoKb2XZOoGTcnCr8%3D&h=169080ed\" target=\"_blank\">https://medium.com/%E9%95%B7%E9%BE%8D%E7%94%B0139%E8%99%9F/%E9%BB%9E%E8%A7%A3%E6%B0%91%E9%99%A3%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C%E9%9B%86%E6%9C%83%E5%AE%8C%E9%83%BD%E4%B8%80%E5%AE%9A%E8%A6%81%E6%95%A3%E6%B0%B4-149e32d0f678?fbclid=IwAR0yZ4ZRBh8b1sA75x7uXFa7RIBP6MF55M0NU1kRGiXddApYHCvizdJaNGs</a><br />\n<br />\n自己睇"},{"pid":"97360c81b0c598a51039ef57c306bc42424620d7","tid":1195522,"uid":259302,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T04:44:49.000Z","msg":"遊行係最正統王統王道嘅方法去表達民意，直接比壓力政權，話比佢地聽佢地嘅基礎動搖緊，好過下下衝，因為一定人少，比政府話你係極少數反動分子，打殘你，到時就無人再衝到。好似打機敢，遊行係升lv(吸引多啲過黎我地呢邊，表達意見)同普攻(遊行本身令政府面對名方壓力)，勇武衝係大技，要睇住mp用，所以要看住迫切性用。<br />\n<br />\n[長文]從共產黨臥底戰術，看香港反送中前路<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1218989\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1218989</a>"},{"pid":"ab70dd2d3c515be3df2bd06018b045a855d7c117","tid":1195522,"uid":82125,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T04:46:08.000Z","msg":"各有各做，各自努力。<br />\n依家民意都好緊要，唔可以比件事掉淡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"512134938f41c45dbd016ddc69bca0587b870fec","tid":1195522,"uid":8883,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T04:47:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f1088563f903ae8f430da88ebc6c23416b400f9","tid":1195522,"uid":12633,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"97360c81b0c598a51039ef57c306bc42424620d7","tid":1195522,"uid":259302,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T04:44:49.000Z","msg":"遊行係最正統王統王道嘅方法去表達民意，直接比壓力政權，話比佢地聽佢地嘅基礎動搖緊，好過下下衝，因為一定人少，比政府話你係極少數反動分子，打殘你，到時就無人再衝到。好似打機敢，遊行係升lv(吸引多啲過黎我地呢邊，表達意見)同普攻(遊行本身令政府面對名方壓力)，勇武衝係大技，要睇住mp用，所以要看住迫切性用。<br />\n<br />\n[長文]從共產黨臥底戰術，看香港反送中前路<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1218989\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1218989</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T04:47:41.000Z","msg":"點解唔直接集會，而係要「行」？"},{"pid":"772daec1c87a7ce6fb65cf